org.ceu.alf.ecollections

Interface CollectionOntologyManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JenaCollectionOntologyManager

    public interface CollectionOntologyManager
    Interface for managing an ontology that uses the E-Collections ontology. This is the main interface and every class that want to access an ontology build with the E-Collections ontology must to implement it.
